'''2015年突厥歌唱大賽'''是第3屆突厥歌唱大賽，主辦國原本為[[土庫曼斯坦|土庫曼斯坦]]但是最後更改至[[土耳其|土耳其]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://eurovoix-world.com/turkvizyon15-contest-moved-to-istanbul/|title = Turkvizyon’15: Contest Moved To Istanbul?|accessdate = 2015-08-26|author = |date = |publisher = |archive-date = 2015-08-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150827013049/http://eurovoix-world.com/turkvizyon15-contest-moved-to-istanbul/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。由土耳其音樂盒電視台規畫。將由28個[[突厥語系|突厥語系]]或者是[[突厥人|突厥人]]多數的國家地區以及兩個族群社團參加，預賽在2015年12月17日舉行，而決賽在19日舉行。<ref name=FinalDate>{{cite web|last1=Granger|first1=Anthony|title=Turkvizyon’15: Final On December 19|url=http://eurovoix-world.com/turkvizyon15-final-on-december-19/|website=eurovoix-world.com|accessdate=2015-10-27|archive-date=2015-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151027235735/http://eurovoix-world.com/turkvizyon15-final-on-december-19/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
