==地點==
{{Details|伊斯坦堡|馬雷|阿什哈巴特}}
2014年11月，官方決定將於土庫曼尼斯坦的[[馬雷市|馬雷市]]舉辦<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://eurovoix.com/2014/11/22/turkvizyon15-mary-will-host-the-contest/|title = Turkvizyon’15: Mary Will Host The Contest|accessdate = 2014-11-22|author = |date = |publisher = |archive-date = 2014-11-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129033228/http://eurovoix.com/2014/11/22/turkvizyon15-mary-will-host-the-contest/|dead-url = no}}</ref>，之後遷移到該國首都[[阿什哈巴特|阿什哈巴特]]舉辦<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://eurovoix.com/2015/02/21/turkvizyon15-contest-to-be-held-in-ashgabat/|title = Turkvizyon’15: Contest To Be Held In Ashgabat|accessdate = 2015-02-21|author = |date = |publisher = |archive-date = 2015-02-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150221193700/http://eurovoix.com/2015/02/21/turkvizyon15-contest-to-be-held-in-ashgabat/|dead-url = no}}</ref>，於2015年八月又遷至土耳其的伊斯坦堡舉行。

比賽將在伊斯坦堡的Yahya Kemal Beyatli 文化中心舉辦。

